        public static SocksProxy parse(String value)
                        throws UnknownHostException,
                               FileNotFoundException
        Creates a SocksProxy instance with a string.
        For example:
        • host,1080 = Socks5.Socks5(String, int)
        • host,1080,root,123456 = Socks5.Socks5(String, int, Credentials)
        • host,1080,root,123456,trustKeystorePath,trustKeyStorePassoword = Creates a SSLSocks5 instance
        • host,1080,root,123456,trustKeystorePath,trustKeyStorePassoword,keystorePath, keystorePathPassword = Creates a SSLSocks5 instance which supports client authentication
        Parameters:
        value - a string.
        Returns:
        a SocksProxy instance.
        Throws:
        UnknownHostException - if the host is unknown.
        FileNotFoundException - if file not found.
